ostejov-hlasi-prvni-pripad-onemocneni-koronavirem-20200310.html|title=Prostejov reports the first case of coronavirus disease|website=prostejovsky.denik.cz|access-date=2020-03-10}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''42'''\n| 10 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}} \n| {{Success|Travel-related}}\n| {{flag|Austria}}\n| {{n/a}}\n| [[Pardubice Region]]\n| {{Success|Home isolation}}\n| Male\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | Elderly man was skiing in [[Bad Gastein]].<ref name=case42>{{cite web|url=https://www.novinky.cz/domaci/clanek/koronavirus-poprve-privezl-lyzar-z-rakouska-hlasi-hygienici-z-pardubic-40316207|title=Koronavirus was first brought by a skier from Austria, reports hygienists from Pardubice|website=novinky.cz|access-date=2020-03-10}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''43'''\n| 10 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}} \n| {{n/a}}\n| {{n/a}}\n| [[Prague]]\n| [[Prague]]\n| {{n/a}}\n| Female\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{n/a}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | Student of V\u0160E in Prague.<ref name=\"case43-61\">{{cite web|url=https://www.idnes.cz/zpravy/domaci/koronavirus-nakzeni-pripady-cesko.A200310_181016_domaci_remy|title=Rapid increase. There are already 61 people infected with new coronavirus in the Czech Republic|website=idnes.cz|access-date=2020-03-10}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''44'''\n| 10 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}} \n| {{n/a}}\n| {{n/a}}\n| [[Prague]]\n| [[Prague]]\n| {{n/a}}\n| Male\n| Child\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | Student of Norbertov elementary school in Prague 6.<ref name=\"case43-61\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''45'''\n| 10 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}} \n| {{Success|Travel-related}}\n| {{flag|Italy}}\n| [[Litovel]]\n| [[Olomouc Region]]\n| {{Partial failure|Hospital in P