 apart from others\n** Associated facilities (showers, changing rooms) remain closed.\n| Government Resolution No. 215/2020 Coll.<ref name=\"FreeMovementBan\">{{cite web|url=https://apps.odok.cz/attachment/-/down/IHOABMQVW63P |title=USNESEN\u00cdVL\u00c1DY \u010cESK\u00c9 REPUBLIKY |publisher=apps.odok.cz |date=2020 |accessdate=2020-04-06}}</ref>\n\nMinistry of Health Protection Measure No. MZDR 12745/2020-1/MIN/KAN<ref name=\"2 people ban\">{{cite web|url=https://www.mzcr.cz/Soubor.ashx?souborID=40682&typ=application/pdf&nazev=Mimo%C5%99%C3%A1dn%C3%A9%20opat%C5%99en%C3%AD%20-%20voln%C3%BD%20pohyb%20osob%20na%20%C3%BAzem%C3%AD%20%C4%8CR.pdf |title=Data |publisher=www.mzcr.cz |date= |accessdate=2020-04-06}}</ref>\n\nMinistry of Health Protection Measure No. MZDR 12745/2020-4/MIN/KAN<ref name=\"2 people ban 2\"/>\n\nMinistry of Health Protection Measure No. MZDR 15190/2020-4/MIN/KAN<ref name=\"sports allowed\">{{cite web|url=https://www.mzcr.cz/Soubor.ashx?souborID=40882&typ=application/pdf&nazev=Mimo%C5%99%C3%A1dn%C3%A9%20opat%C5%99en%C3%AD%20-%20omezen%C3%AD%20pohybu%20osob%20s%20v%C3%BDjimkami.pdf |title=Sports allowed |publisher=www.mzcr.cz |date= |accessdate=2020-04-08}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''Regional quarantine'''\n| Quarantine of town of '''[[Litovel]]''' and 18 nearby municipalities including '''[[Uni\u010dov]]''' and '''[[\u010cervenka (Olomouc District)|\u010cervenka]]'''.\n\nThe quarantine zone covers about 24,000 people. A cluster of 25 patients identified on 16 March 2020. By 21 March 2020 there were 54 confirmed patients within the quarantine zone out of 62 total confirmed cases in [[Olomouc region]].\n| 16 March 2020\n| From 16 March onwards (indefinitely).\n\n'''Lifted on 30 March 2020'''\n| People living and working within the quarantined area can go to work.\n\nPeople living within the area and working outside, and vice versa, must stay at home.\n\nWorkers returning from night shifts in the area to homes outside of the area ordered into 14 days' self-quarantine.\n\nPolice checkpoints on roads to the area. Only supply trucks, police, emergency, and fire rescue service can enter/leave town.\n\nMilitary field mini-hospital build in Litovel on 19 March.<ref>{{cite web|author=Autor: Jakub Fajnor, tiskov\u00e9 odd\u011blen\u00ed MO |url=http://www.acr.army.cz/informacni-servis/covid/nasazeni-prislusniku-armady-cr-a-vojenske-policie-v-obci-litovel-220237/ |title=V Litovli na Olomoucku jsou ode dne\u0161ka nasazeni p\u0159\u00edslu\u0161n\u00edci Arm\u00e1dy \u010cR a Vojensk\u00e9 policie &#124; Ministerstvo obrany |publisher=Acr.army.cz |date=2020-03-19 |accessdate=2020-04-06}}</ref>\n| Local health authority.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.idnes.cz/olomouc/zpravy/koronavirus-unicov-litovel-cervenka.A200316_062222_olomouc-zpravy_jadv|title=Hygienici zav\u0159eli Litovel, Uni\u010dov a 19 obc\u00ed. V izolaci je 24 tis\u00edc lid\u00ed|date=16 March 2020|website=iDNES.cz}}</ref>\n|-\n| Quarantine of municipality of '''[[Kynice]]''', where a number of people were infected during the local volunteer fire department's ball.\n\nThe municipality has a population of 95.\n| 16 March 2020\n| From 16 March onwards (indefinitely).\n\n'''Lifted on 1 April 2020'''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.irozhlas.cz/zpravy-domov/kynice-izolace-konec-karanteny-koronavirus-hasici-dezinfekce_2004011116_tzr |title=Kynice opou\u0161t\u00ed po dvou t\u00fddnech karant\u00e9nu. V izolaci z\u016fst\u00e1vaj\u00ed pouze nemocn\u00ed, hasi\u010di \u010d\u00e1sti obce dezinfikuj\u00ed &#124; iROZHLAS - spolehliv\u00e9 zpr\u00e1vy |publisher=Irozhlas.cz |date=2020-04-01 |accessdate=2020-04-06}}</ref>\n| Same conditions as in other quaranteened areas.\n| Local health authority.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.novinky.cz/zahranicni/koronavirus/clanek/hygienici-zcela-uzavreli-kynici-kde-se-virus-rozsiril-na-hasicske-zabave-40316848|title=Hygienici zcela uzav\u0159eli Kynice, kde se virus roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159il na hasi\u010dsk\u00e9 z\u00e1bav\u011b - Novinky.cz|website=www.novinky.cz}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=6 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''Social distancing measures'''\n| '''Public authorities' activity reduction'''\n| 12 March 2020\n| 14 March to 1 April.\n\nExtended until 11 April.\n| Public authorities restricted to perform only to necessary duties. Restrictions on duties requiring personal contact with the public. Restriction of office hours to 3 hours on Monday and Wednesday. Only the lowest possible number of employees to be present when necessary. Duty to implement rotations of employees in a way that prevents contact between selected groups.\n\n'''Partially revoked on 6 April 2020''': {{Interlanguage link|Czechpoint|cs|Czech POINT}} resumes service.\n| Government Resolution No. 194/2000 (until 24 March)\n\nMinistry of Health Protection Measure No. MZDR 12745/2020-3/MIN/KAN (from 24 March onwards)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mzcr.cz/Soubor.ashx?souborID=40684&typ=application/pdf&nazev=Mimo%C5%99%C3%A1dn%C3%A9%20opat%C5%99en%C3%AD%20-%20prodlou%C5%BEen%C3%AD%20omezen%C3%AD%20%C4%8Dinnosti%20OVM%20a%20SO.pdf |title=Info |publisher=www.mzcr.cz |date= |accessdate=2020-04-06}}</ref>\n\nMinistry of Health Protection Measure No. MZDR 12745/2020-5/MIN/KAN (from 1 April onwards)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mzcr.cz/Soubor.ashx?souborID=40760&typ=application/pdf&nazev=Mimo%C5%99%C3%A1dn%C3%A9%20opat%C5%99en%C3%AD%20-%20prodlou%C5%BEen%C3%AD%20na%C5%99%C3%ADzen%C3%AD%20omezen%C3%A9ho%20provozu%20OVM%20a%20SO.pdf |title=Info |publisher=www.mzcr.cz |date= |accessdate=2020-04-06}}</ref>\n\nMinistry of Health Protection Measure No. MZDR 15190/2020-2/MIN/KAN (Czechpoint reopening)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mzcr.cz/Soubor.ashx?souborID=40880&typ=application/pdf&nazev=Ukon%C4%8Den%C3%AD%20mimo%C5%99%C3%A1dn%C3%A9ho%20opat%C5%99en%C3%AD%20ze%20dne%2030.%203.%202020%20ke%20kontaktn%C3%ADm%20m%C3%ADst%C5%AFm%20ve%C5%99ejn%C3%A9%20spr%C3%A1vy%20Czech%20POI